  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Weapon Preference: Phaser<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The Yor resemble beetles or cockroaches of Earth.<o:=
p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The Yor rarely communicate with others and seem to v=
alue
  spreading themselves out to other planets above all else.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Yor are not very intelligent but do work well in gro=
ups.
  They do not have a concept of copyright or patent. Stealing ideas is
  acceptable, advancement in technology comes about because of a common dri=
ve
  towards their own races power not personal gain.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The Yor have years of knowledge of phaser beam techn=
ology
  and have adapted their phaser technology to work on star fighter scale. T=
he
  Yor Stinger Beam gains more range than comparable Phasers, allowing them =
to
  strike first before the enemy has realized they are upon them.<o:p></o:p>=
</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The Yor can be found in the driest deserts, their ha=
bitats
  built upon the sand. These hovels are usually swarming with Yor who do not
  seem to mind overpopulation levels others would find unbearable.</p>
